{"tid":1363494,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"727 入元朗唔搞人祠堂/山墳，其實有國際性考慮，尤其要顧住臺灣！","createTime":"2019-07-25T07:55:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-26T16:54:39.000Z","uid":217196,"like":30,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"c6e5caed36a062e51dee6bdc86f7bb37bf5136db","tid":1363494,"uid":217196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T07:55:07.000Z","msg":"你地知唔知世界上其他華人社會，尤其臺灣啲人有幾迷信？<br />\n<br />\n我喺臺灣住過三年，佢地好多人都迷信到一個地步，普通香港人係好難想像嘅。<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">而家唔是講緊啲老人家，係十來廿歲果啲，大家夢眛以求嘅臺妹，都會信媽祖，病左會去飲符水果種呀。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n宜家，全個地球，尤其各地華人社會都企喺香港人呢邊。<br />\n<br />\n人地出黑社會打我地，我地覆桌係天公地道。打死無怨。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">但如果搞人地祖先，就係爛仔、懦夫嘅所為，而且會令全球華人社會反感。尤其臺灣呢個咁迷信嘅地方，對呢啲「有損陰德」嘅事真係好反感。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n到時搞到蔡英文都同我地割蓆就灰。 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b4b02c74afbef23b42ef2a26a357c84617eeab1","tid":1363494,"uid":217196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T07:57:58.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"4e3fe9cdb69fe8823a2d1d8fd70edcfe0b3cbbed","tid":1363494,"uid":217196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T07:58:30.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"897902247a77ad5bc0ba1b9be6cbbb5e6e850860","tid":1363494,"uid":2526,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T07:59:42.000Z","msg":"集中焦點打黑社會<br />\n好多外姓人搬左入村係事實<br />\n真正村民好多都搬左出去<br />\n集中對付酒吧，色情場所，違泊<br />\n斷佢地收入最直接"},{"pid":"6cd90c7625469d90da3f68f652d8abcf8c2b00b5","tid":1363494,"uid":263344,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T08:11:41.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n我都知台灣人真係好撚迷信<br />\n仲有一樣，民進黨好想拉攏台灣原住民既票。如果我今次攪人圍村，蔡英文既對手實會借機會屈到變成蔡英文支持既人會攪原住民。咁到時我地就害左蔡英文啦！"},{"pid":"22203a5d72178f17223f4e45be51da7c28dc745b","tid":1363494,"uid":217196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T08:36:26.000Z","msg":"我無野講"},{"pid":"df0e5a0fa52699a3a5dbf61dc40bf90c88a992d7","tid":1363494,"uid":127269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T08:43:21.000Z","msg":"樓主講得啱<br />\n所以係反黑 係何妖唔找數<br />\n用字要清楚"},{"pid":"f5cd9f4e23cc036e7530eb9f509d76c953399410","tid":1363494,"uid":217196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T07:27:17.000Z","msg":"我無野講"},{"pid":"f41d493f200f44f79489dd2fec218a9b57f3316a","tid":1363494,"uid":260639,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T12:58:25.000Z","msg":"呢個角度好好"},{"pid":"867c356fa8d0a1d9fd609bdc0e1b9f22892b2868","tid":1363494,"uid":138934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T13:13:22.000Z","msg":"我無野講"},{"pid":"3d6e41bc074768aa2bc3ce856d6b01ebd6812ca4","tid":1363494,"uid":217196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T16:53:21.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"e4d4e591b801ef5ca31f9ed7da9bf9699497eaa7","tid":1363494,"uid":9315,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T16:54:39.000Z","msg":"聽日警黑夾攻示威者<br />\n講真就算真係攻我都唔覺入到去  更何況部分人係唔打算入<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}